Mantega Says Brazil’s Inflation Rate Will Begin to Fall

-- B y   M a t t h e w   B r i s t o w
-- 
2011-09-23T15:01:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-23/mantega-says-brazil-s-inflation-rate-will-begin-to-fall.html
Brazil ’s inflation rate will fall
close to the government’s target in line with a decline in price
increases globally, Finance Minister  Guido Mantega  said at an
event today in  Washington .  Mantega said Brazil’s inflation isn’t so bad compared with
other nations in the world.  To contact the reporter on this story:
